Ving Rhames, who's starred as Luther Stickell in every "Mission: Impossible" film, had a cameo in Marvel's 2017 film "Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2."
On the left: Ving Rhames in "Mission: Impossible — Dead Reckoning Part One." On the right: Rhames in "Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2." Paramount Pictures;
He appeared as the character Charlie-27 toward the end of the film, as a nod to the original lineup of "Guardians of the Galaxy" from 1969.
